# Local-only and secrets — never commit
*.local
*.local.md
CLAUDE.local.md
.env
.env.*
!.env.template
**/secret*
**/*secret*
# Exception: this rule DOC explains the secrets-as-references policy and holds NO secret
# values; the globs above would wrongly exclude it. It is one of the 7 always-loaded global
# rules and MUST be tracked + synced, so re-include it explicitly.
!**/secrets-as-references.md
*.key
*.pem
.DS_Store
scratch/
tmp/
